c: 4
v: 119
t: "Ne toto nditsa okhubakosia nende okhubasubisia nende okhubalomesia shingala ndenya, mana betsa okhuteta amarwi ketsisolo, Ne nditsa okhubalomesia bakalukhanie obulonji bwa Nyasaye, Ne ukhola shetani okhuba omulindi wuwe owulali Nyasaye, awo aba asishile (atibile) okhusikha khwa habulafu"